reviews.text: Friendly + tentative staff. They are very used to kids so they know what younglings+parents need. We've always loved their fresh waffles + signature coffees. Other dishes such as pastas and sandwich are decent too.
a Japanese style cafe with waffle, italian, ice scream, and siphon coffees. UCC group is a leader and evangelist in siphon, but not necessarily every shop though.

If you come at afternoon, you can enjoy The Afternoon Tea sets with spaghetti or waffle with coffee.
I highly recommend this restaurant but you need to be patient as there are not much tables and it usually take 30 to 45 mins to wait.
Good quality. Note that there will be minimum charge for each person ($120) during weekends.
Tasteless coffee I ever have. Absolutely ripoff!
